%% PWA Feasibility Decision Flow
%% Helps decide when PWA is viable vs when native is required

flowchart TD
    A[New App Project] --> B{Need App Store listing?}
    B -->|Yes, required| C{Need background processing?}
    B -->|No / optional| D{Need native OS features?}

    C -->|Yes| E[Native or Capacitor Hybrid]
    C -->|No| F{Budget / timeline constraint?}
    F -->|Tight budget| G[Capacitor Hybrid]
    F -->|Flexible| E

    D -->|System tray, shortcuts, deep OS| H[Tauri / Electron / Native]
    D -->|No native OS needed| I{What type of app?}

    I --> J{Content / E-commerce / MVP?}
    J -->|Yes| K[✅ PWA — Best Fit]

    I --> L{Uber-type / ride-sharing?}
    L -->|Rider app| M[⚠️ PWA for MVP → Capacitor for prod]
    L -->|Driver app| N[❌ PWA not viable → Native required]

    I --> O{Game?}
    O --> P{Game type?}
    P -->|Casual / 2D / Puzzle| Q[✅ PWA — Excellent Fit]
    P -->|3D Mid-tier| R[⚠️ PWA possible with WebGPU + WASM]
    P -->|AAA 3D / Competitive FPS| S[❌ PWA not viable → Native engine]

    I --> T{Internal business tool?}
    T -->|Yes| K

    style K fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style Q fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style M fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style R fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style N fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
    style S fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
    style E fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style H fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style G fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
